{"tid":448084,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony Xperia XZ Premium 鏡紅新色開賣，Android 8.0 更新開始","createTime":"2017-10-26T01:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T02:56:37.000Z","uid":141060,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"241038ad6e54e52a51932ffd5c16c94333e73d76","tid":448084,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T01:45:33.000Z","msg":"Sony Xperia XZ Premium 鏡紅新色開賣<br />\nSony Mobile 剛剛在上週於日本發表 Xperia XZ Premium 的「Rosso 鏡紅」新色款式，才隔了一週，Sony Mobile 也在今（25）日宣佈，XZ Premium 鏡紅新色將於即日起在台推出，單機建議售價 22,900 元，比起先前降了 2,000 元，並將於 11 月 1 日起於五大電信門市上架。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Sony Mobile 也宣佈，除了鏡紅新色推出時就內建 Android 8.0 Oreo 系統外，已販售的 Xperia XZ Premium 也將在很快的時間升級 Android 8.0，升級後將加入與 Xperia XZ1 / XZ1 Compact 相同的微笑預拍、3D 即時掃描以及自動追焦連拍功能。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/094528_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F094528_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=212ebf12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/094528_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F094528_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=42cd5b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/094529_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F094529_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=cdb24824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/26/094529_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F26%2F094529_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=65f41d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/2